description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.datadoghq.com/tracing/&quot;&gt;Application Performance Monitoring&lt;/a&gt; (APM) is one of Datadog’s premier products that helps developers see inside complex distributed systems. Our SDKs are both the delivery vehicle for APM and the platform on which all of Datadog’s service and app based products (e.g. Application Security Management, Profiling, Data Stream Monitoring…) are delivered. We believe our SDKs are one of our technical moats and are a key competitive advantage for APM and Datadog more broadly. They’re also open-source.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leading the evolution of our SDKs is a technically demanding and highly collaborative effort. You’ll work with language experts to deliver cutting-edge observability products across our 9 supported languages, with industry leading performance and a world class developer experience. You’ll rethink our SDKs’ architecture, APIs, data models, and protocol to meet Datadog’s current needs and scale, all while building in the open. And you’ll grow your team’s capacity by fostering a culture focused on customer needs, continuous learning, and innovation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an experienced Engineering Manager who cares as much about technical excellence as empowering other engineering teams.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;At Datadog, we place value in our office culture - the relationships that it builds, the creativity it brings to the table, and the collaboration of being together. We operate as a hybrid workplace to ensure our employees can create a work-life harmony that best fits them.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead a team of Engineers and collaborate with Product teams to:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reshape and grow our platform capabilities to enable product teams&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and deliver industry leading, open-source, zero-touch APM instrumentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set a high standard for quality and invest in the tooling and process to maintain it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own outcomes, from the quality of implementation to the quality of the user experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep up to date with the cutting edge of observability instrumentation in industry to ensure Datadog remains a leader in the category&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An experienced Engineering Manager with a track record of shipping&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong and empathetic leader with the ability to build and lead high-performing teams to deliver high quality software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An ability pivot from high level product narratives to highly technical implementation details&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have significant programming experience in one or more of: Java, Go, Ruby&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bonus&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt; If you possess experience with one or more of these skills: systems programming experience, observability tooling experience, experience shipping client side software, JVM, Go or Ruby runtime expertise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Datadog values people from all walks of life. We understand not everyone will meet all the above qualifications on day one. That&#39;s okay. If you’re passionate about technology and want to grow your skills, we encourage you to apply.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits and Growth:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New hire stock equity (RSUs) and employee stock purchase plan (ESPP)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuous professional development, product training, and career pathing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intradepartmental mentor and buddy program for in-house networking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An inclusive company culture, ability to join our Community Guilds (Datadog employee resource groups)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to Inclusion Talks, our Internal panel discussions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free, global mental health benefits for employees and dependents age 6+&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive global benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Benefits and Growth listed above may vary based on the country of your employment and the nature of your employment with Datadog.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Datadog offers a competitive salary and equity package, and may include variable compensation. Actual compensation is based on factors such as the candidate&#39;s skills, qualifications, and experience. In addition, Datadog offers a wide range of best in class, comprehensive and inclusive employee benefits for this role including healthcare, dental, parental planning, and mental health benefits, a 401(k) plan and match, paid time off, fitness reimbursements, and a discounted employee stock purchase plan.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;The reasonably estimated yearly salary for this role at Datadog is:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$187,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$240,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Datadog:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Datadog (NASDAQ: DDOG) is a global SaaS business, delivering a rare combination of growth and profitability. We are on a mission to break down silos and solve complexity in the cloud age by enabling digital transformation, cloud migration, and infrastructure monitoring of our customers’ entire technology stacks. Built by engineers, for engineers, Datadog is used by organizations of all sizes across a wide range of industries. Together, we champion professional development, diversity of thought, innovation, and work excellence to empower continuous growth. Join the pack and become part of a collaborative, pragmatic, and thoughtful people-first community where we solve tough problems, take smart risks, and celebrate one another. Learn more about #DatadogLife on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/datadoghq/?hl=en&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/datadog&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;LinkedIn,&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://learn.datadoghq.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Datadog Learning Center. &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;215&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Equal Opportunity at Datadog:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Datadog is proud to offer &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2023-06/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights6.12ScreenRdr.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;equal employment opportunity&lt;/a&gt; to everyone regardless of race, color, ancestry, religion, sex, national origin, sexual orientation, age, citizenship, marital status, disability, gender identity, veteran status, and other characteristics protected by law. We also consider qualified applicants regardless of criminal histories, consistent with legal requirements. Here are our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.datadoghq.com/legal/candidate-legal-notices/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Candidate Legal Notices&lt;/a&gt; for your reference.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Datadog endeavors to make our Careers Page accessible to all users. If you would like to contact us regarding the accessibility of our website or need assistance completing the application process, please complete &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeoJeduEZ2NdZF_65uZmWUrCM-zee7yADXX1s6Xr9zAGq8iKA/viewform&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;this form&lt;/a&gt;. This form is for accommodation requests only and cannot be used to inquire about the status of applications.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;662&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Privacy and AI Guidelines:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;662&quot;&gt;Any information you submit to Datadog as part of your application will be processed in accordance with Datadog’s&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.datadoghq.com/legal/applicant-candidate-privacy/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.datadoghq.com/legal/applicant-candidate-privacy/&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;Applicant and Candidate Privacy Notice&lt;/a&gt;. For information on our AI policy, please visit &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.datadoghq.com/legal/interviewing-at-datadog-ai-guidelines/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Interviewing at Datadog AI Guidelines&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At Datadog, we’re on a mission to bring security and observability together for modern organizations.&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/bits-ai-security-analyst/&quot;&gt; Bits AI for Security&lt;/a&gt; is our AI-powered assistant that leverages large language models (LLMs) to help analysts investigate alerts, understand threats, and respond faster. We’re looking for an Engineering Manager I to lead the team building the next generation of AI-driven security capabilities.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to combine security expertise with GenAI/LLM innovation, helping shape how AI empowers security analysts worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;At Datadog, we place value in our office culture - the relationships that it builds, the creativity it brings to the table, and the collaboration of being together. We operate as a hybrid workplace to ensure our employees can create a work-life harmony that best fits them.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and grow a talented engineering team working at the intersection of security, AI, and product innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with product managers, security experts, and AI researchers to design and deliver AI Agents (LLM-powered) that drive real value for our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide the team in building production-ready systems that combine Datadog’s security platform with GenAI models, agents, and retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and develop senior engineers and managers, fostering a culture of high performance, inclusion, and psychological safety&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the delivery of critical product initiatives, ensuring technical excellence, reliability, and alignment with Datadog’s high bar for security.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in hiring and organizational planning for future growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote best practices in machine learning, AI engineering, operational standards, and career development across the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An experienced technical leader with a strong background in AI, machine learning, or data science&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading and mentoring multiple teams, including senior engineers and engineering managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledgeable about LLM technologies (prompt engineering, fine-tuning, RAG, agents) and how to apply them in real-world, production-grade systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with backend or full-stack development in a cloud-based SaaS environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong in communication and collaboration, able to align engineers, product managers, and researchers around shared goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong people manager, able to attract, develop, and retain top AI and engineering talent&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excited to work in the security domain, with an understanding of how analysts investigate threats and alerts (security background is a strong plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with LLM frameworks (LangChain, LlamaIndex, OpenAI API, Hugging Face, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributions to AI/ML infrastructure or applied GenAI products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience scaling products in a high-growth SaaS environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Why You Should Apply:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll be at the forefront of AI applied to security, shaping how analysts use GenAI to work smarter and faster.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll lead a highly motivated team at Datadog, collaborating across product, AI research, and security domains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll have the chance to work on cutting-edge GenAI/LLM challenges with real-world impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;Datadog values people from all walks of life. We understand not everyone will meet all the above qualifications on day one. That&#39;s okay. If you’re passionate about technology and want to grow your skills, we encourage you to apply.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits and Growth:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New hire stock equity (RSUs) and employee stock purchase plan (ESPP)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuous professional development, product training, and career pathing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intradepartmental mentor and buddy program for in-house networking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An inclusive company culture, ability to join our Community Guilds (Datadog employee resource groups)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to Inclusion Talks, our Internal panel discussions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free, global mental health benefits for employees and dependents age 6+&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive global benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Benefits and Growth listed above may vary based on the country of your employment and the nature of your employment with Datadog.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;To conform to US export control regulations, candidates should be eligible for any required authorizations from the US government. This job is available in various departments within our company; to conform to US export control regulations, some of these roles may require candidates to be eligible for any required authorizations from the US government.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Datadog offers a competitive salary and equity package, and may include variable compensation. Actual compensation is based on factors such as the candidate&#39;s skills, qualifications, and experience. In addition, Datadog offers a wide range of best in class, comprehensive and inclusive employee benefits for this role including healthcare, dental, parental planning, and mental health benefits, a 401(k) plan and match, paid time off, fitness reimbursements, and a discounted employee stock purchase plan.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;The reasonably estimated yearly salary for this role at Datadog is:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$234,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$300,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Datadog:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Datadog (NASDAQ: DDOG) is a global SaaS business, delivering a rare combination of growth and profitability. We are on a mission to break down silos and solve complexity in the cloud age by enabling digital transformation, cloud migration, and infrastructure monitoring of our customers’ entire technology stacks. Built by engineers, for engineers, Datadog is used by organizations of all sizes across a wide range of industries. Together, we champion professional development, diversity of thought, innovation, and work excellence to empower continuous growth. Join the pack and become part of a collaborative, pragmatic, and thoughtful people-first community where we solve tough problems, take smart risks, and celebrate one another. Learn more about #DatadogLife on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/datadoghq/?hl=en&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/datadog&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;LinkedIn,&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://learn.datadoghq.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Datadog Learning Center. &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
